definitions.definition: Any of various freshwater fish of the family Cyprinidae ; specifically the common carp , Cyprinus carpio .

main_definition: Any of various freshwater fish of the family Cyprinidae ; specifically the common carp , Cyprinus carpio .

definitions.definition: An instance of, or speech , complaining or criticizing about a fault , especially for frivolous or petty reasons ; a cavil .
